Personal Life:
Despite her demanding career, Olivia places a strong emphasis on maintaining a healthy work-life balance. She enjoys spending quality time with her close-knit circle of friends and family, engaging in activities such as hosting dinner parties, attending cultural events, and traveling to explore new destinations. Olivia is also an active supporter of various philanthropic causes, dedicating both her time and resources to making a positive impact in her community.

